                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                    <h6 class="section-title text-start text-primary text-uppercase mb-4">Contact</h6>
                    <p class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-map-marker-alt me-3"></i>Kiten, Provadia, Bulgaria</p>
                    <p class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-phone-alt me-3"></i>+359 894417277</p>
